net.smartcosmos.objects.model.context

Interface ILibraryElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAccountContext, IAccountDomainResource<ILibraryElement>, IDomainResource<ILibraryElement>, IMoniker, INamedObject<ILibraryElement>, ITypedObject, IUrnNamespace
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LibraryElement

    public interface ILibraryElement
extends IAccountDomainResource<ILibraryElement>, INamedObject<ILibraryElement>, ITypedObject
    Foundational artifact within the SMART COSMOS Objects platform used to represent nouns, e.g. people, bank accounts, vehicles, parks, buildings, etc.

    All objects are INamedObject instances so that a human-readable INamedObject.getName() can be assigned.

    The library element type is distinct from other INamedObject types in that the Type field is always set to "LibraryElement", and cannot be changed. The field "LibraryElementType" is specific to LibraryElements, and is set to one of the values specified in the LibraryHierarchy section of objects.yml.
